PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEID, PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPEDESC, CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.STYLESHEETNAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_TEMPLATE.OUTPUTFORMAT FROM PSX_TEMPLATE, CONTENTTYPES, PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE CTT WHERE CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTTYPEID = CTT.CONTENTTYPEID AND CTT.TEMPLATE_ID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID AND PSX_TEMPLATE.OUTPUTFORMAT IN (:"PSXSingleParam/outputformat") AND PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID NOT IN(SELECT RXSLOTCONTENT.VARIANTID FROM RXSLOTCONTENT WHERE RXSLOTCONTENT.SLOTID=:"PSXParam/slotid") ORDER BY CONTENTTYPES.CONTENTTYPENAME ASC
